d this piece in late 2008. For this work, I aimed to convey both the industrial heaviness of an airplane, but also the cloudlike floating quality you feel when you’re in one.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->', 'Today\'s our team\'s discovering', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '50-revision-v1', '', '', '2023-02-11 21:47:16', '2023-02-11 19:47:16', '', 50, 'http://localhost/Projects/Wordpress/wordpress-23/?p=51', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
